{"tid":2123142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王毅：中國絕不容許毫無底線的美國亂來！","createTime":"2020-07-24T12:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T13:27:07.000Z","uid":7542,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"faa117482c3ef92a238cba1f2dfff2a196acf726","tid":2123142,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"國務委員兼外長王毅與德國外長馬斯舉行視像會談。王毅表示，中美關係目前面臨的困難，完全是美方一手造成，<strong>目的就是企圖徹底打斷中國發展進程，為此可以不擇手段，甚至毫無底線。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bi31fcs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBi31fcs.jpg&h=6d94783f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王毅批評，美方一些反華勢力近期蓄意製造意識形態對立，公開脅迫別國選邊站隊，為了美方的私利與中國對抗，但任何有良知及獨立精神的國家，都不會與之為伍。<br />\n<br />\n王毅表示，中國仍然希與美國實現不衝突、不對抗、相互尊重、合作共贏，<strong>但中方必將堅定維護國家主權與民族尊嚴</strong>，堅定維護自身正當發展權利，堅定維護國際關係基本準則，<strong>中國不會隨美方起舞，但亦絕不容許美方亂來</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539714-20200724.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539714-20200724.htm&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=50574a58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539714-20200724.htm&h=016beec6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539714-20200724.htm</a>"},{"pid":"057dc2ecea801a1ca95b4f9479c06a50dcc51e58","tid":2123142,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79138ecd8139a48d56350f0e7ff285731757bb6","tid":2123142,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:10:50.000Z","msg":"自己亂來就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed7f01a8c1f85986f1c